IRS990.ActivityOrMissionDesc: There is no restriction for creative activity. Imagination has complete freedom. Supporting and promoting freedom in creativity is KANEKO's mission. Creativity begins with an idea - seeing things differently. Our purpose is exploring the creative process.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: Form 990, Part VI, Line 11b: Form 990 Review Process
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: Once Form 990 is prepared, it is emailed to the members of the governing body for their review. Any suggestions or changes that are necessary are then made to Form 990.
